title: Sheikh Mohammed tours marine exhibition area at NAVDEX

persons.name: hamdan bin mohammed bin rashid al maktoum

text:
Sheikh Mohammed tours marine exhibition area at NAVDEX By Published Tuesday, February 21, 2017 
His Highness Sheikh Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum, Vice President, Prime Minister and Ruler of Dubai, accompanied by Crown Prince of Dubai Sheikh Hamdan bin Mohammed bin Rashid Al Maktoum, toured today the marine exhibition area at NAVDEX, the naval defence and maritime security section of the tri-service International Defence Exhibition and Conference, IDEX 2017. 
More than 100 firms are exhibiting in at NAVDEX, including local, Arab and international firms, where His Highness was briefed about the advanced military equipment and techniques. Share with a friend or colleague Your e-mail address:
